g of wisdom and a model for philosophers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 03. Jan 2023) 7aPHILOSOPHY / Religious.2bisacsh1 aKennedy, Eugene, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertFordham University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014z978311118960408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertFordham University Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311070729840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978082329558640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780823295586423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780823295586/original  a978-3-11-070729-8  Fordham University Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  a978-3-11-118960-4  Fordham University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014b2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK